## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **eculizumab Soliris 2017** = first FDA C5 mAb gMG AChR Ab+ (REGAIN trial). complement-mediated NMJ destruction 차단 paradigm 첫 입증. quantum-VQE 의 C5 protein-protein interaction scaffold fit.
2. **efgartigimod Vyvgart 2021** = first FDA FcRn antagonist (ADAPT trial). IgG-lowering 으로 자가항체 자체 감소 paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 FcRn-IgG Fc pocket leverage 첫 입증.
3. **zilucoplan Zilbrysq 2023** = first FDA C5 small-molecule SC daily (RAISE trial). mAb 의 small-molecule replacement = 양자-VQE 의 사례 매칭.
4. **rozanolixizumab Rystiggo 2023 + nipocalimab Imaavy 2024** = FcRn 2nd + 3rd 승인. AChR + MuSK 광범위 + pediatric MG (Vivacity-MG) 첫 FDA = pediatric-specific 적응증.
5. **efgartigimod alfa SC (Vyvgart Hytrulo) 2023** = first SC FcRn — IV → SC 편의성 paradigm.
6. **pyridostigmine Mestinon 1955** = 만성 AChE 흡억 1L symptomatic — 70+ 년 1L 표준. cross-POTS 동일 약물 다른 적응증 = drug-repurposing 사례.
7. **rituximab off-label** = MuSK Ab+ refractory MG 효과 — but on-label 미승인. RCT ineffective in AChR Ab+ — Ab subtype-stratified treatment paradigm.
8. **thymectomy** = paraneoplastic + thymoma + thymic hyperplasia — surgical 만성 disease-modifying. MGTX RCT 2016 = thymectomy + prednisone vs prednisone alone superiority 입증.
9. **응급 cholinergic crisis vs myasthenic crisis** = atropine + AChE 약물 differential — cross-emergency_medicine + nerve agent organophosphate cross-environmental.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, MG 임상 의미 한정. K-MG (한국 MG 임상) + 식약처 + 보험 산정특례 = 정책 cross-link 만.

